-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/M%E1%BA%A1i-bi-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-V%C3%A3n-kh%E1%BB%9Fi/poem-3zqHXH5kcFe7DPAC5XNetg">Mại bi đường - Vãn khởi - 邁陂塘－晚起</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-ZzgazbvW_31Yn18OxsV6nA">Tùng Thiện Vương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Huy%E1%BB%81n-Quang-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/T%E1%BA%A3o-thu/poem-vPiKQm9qOlsltyuTC6tPvQ">Tảo thu - 早秋</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Huy%E1%BB%81n-Quang-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-ky6a-6Hq9AEiujrHK0DNTQ">Huyền Quang thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Ngao/poem-w_OMVHVuiVnLMUqZGoDfZg">Thượng Ngao - 上嶅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/author-ZuzXfGup2XR6D9EtGGYzeQ">Phạm Sư Mạnh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%83n-Anh/T%E1%BB%ADu-tuy%E1%BB%81n-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-_ZgchEjBf1StanM6dnFd8w">Tửu tuyền tử - 酒泉子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%83n-Anh/author-to-UkdFjJeg6pwDSfG5oNA">Ngô Văn Anh</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
